1.name: wordpress/be-it-facebook-sidetab
1.description:
Have you been frustrated over where to put your Facebook like box … now your worries are over.

With Be-It Facebook Slide tab you can now choose where on left or right side you want to have your like box floated. You can change hight from top and also slide in and out time. You can also change your tab image to one that fits you.
